#: .\apps\progress\templates\progress\srs.html:20
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The SRS method (Spaced Repetition System) is a\n"
#| "                            spaced repetition approach that helps you "
#| "memorize information effectively and\n"
#| "                            retain it for a long time."
msgid ""
"The SRS method (Spaced Repetition System) is\n"
"                            a\n"
"                            spaced repetition approach that helps you "
"memorize information effectively and\n"
"                            retain it for a long time."
msgstr ""
"Метод SRS (Spaced Repetition System) — это система интервальных повторений,\n"
"которая помогает эффективно запоминать информацию\n"
"и сохранять её в памяти надолго."

#: .\apps\progress\templates\progress\srs.html:26
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "SRS is based on the scientific principle that information should be "
#| "reviewed as rarely as possible,\n"
#| "                            but before it is forgotten. Reviews happen at "
#| "increasing intervals,\n"
#| "                            adapted to how well you have remembered the "
#| "material."
msgid ""
"SRS is based on the scientific principle that information should be "
"reviewed\n"
"                                as rarely as possible,\n"
"                                but before it is forgotten. Reviews happen "
"at increasing intervals,\n"
"                                adapted to how well you have remembered the "
"material."
msgstr ""
"SRS основана на научном принципе: информацию следует повторять как можно "
"реже,\n"
"но до того, как она будет забыта. Повторения происходят через "
"увеличивающиеся интервалы,\n"
"которые подстраиваются под то, насколько хорошо вы усвоили материал."

